<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Na Lung A Awi Kei Nam ?</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mihiemte hinna hi banga hia ahim ?
 Meipi chawmcha hung kilanga mangkit bang hi ahi;
 Simlei pakcha hawih lunlai atuoi bangin,
 Mihiem phatlai paklun zamuol a liem paisek hi.

[V2]
 Aw, na khawvel hinna a beih tieng,
 Bang lampi ahim, na hawh ding?
 Na kumsawt mun ding na gel tieng leh,
 Na lung a awi kei nam?

[V3]
 2. Hun leh tui luong laiin kuomah angak ngei puoi,
 Mitphet kalsungle chawllo in zamuol aliem zing ui;
 Khawvel ahin aum den ding a um puoi,
 Khuolzin nichuong phet I hiu I leisiet hin khuo hi.

[V4]
 3. Na vanglai leh phatlai nihaw a vak sung hin.
 Krista haw'n khawvel pakhawih chenin muong mahleh chunle
 Aw thihna luiguom thim nahawh tieng chu leh,
 Krista lo a muongtaka chiehpai ni kinem maw?

[V5]
 4. Pak zel unau lei nawpna haw su hawih dingin,
 Kumsawt hinna lampi mansak theih na din ei themsek
 Zui in pet mangsan ta leng I van lampiu,
 Tuoikit untin I chan uh lungkham kah leh mauna.

[V6]
 5. Sietlei ah kipahna nawpna, hawl mahleu hing,
 Lunggil leh ngaihtuohna mangin na theihna haw cheng tawh;
 Bangtik kipahna tawplo na mu thei dem?
 Mu ngei puonla Kalvari tuichim na tun ma chun.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>298</hymn_number>
</song>